Package: fdisf
Version: 0.1.20260713
Date: 2026-07-13
Title: Spatial features for fisheries data interoperability
Description: Provides spatial features for fisheries data interoperability, including GIS functions of interest not available in other R spatial-based packages,
 and utilities for handling bounding boxes, vertices, and grids.
